title: Tuna Patties
directions: Stir everything together in a medium mixing bowl until well combined.
Form small patties with your hands (about 1 1/2 inches in diameter).
Cook in a skillet using a heart healthy oil.
ingredients: 4 (5 oz.) cans water packed tuna, no added salt, water drained
2 tablespoons lemon juice (about 1/2 a large lemon)
